---
title: Saucy Louisiana Beef & Bean Burrito Bowl with Garlic Rice & Salsa
description: Tonight, put together a bountiful bowl full of Louisiana flavours! With spiced beans, beef, fresh salsa and fragrant rice, every bite of
this bright meal is as good as the next!
